		</li>
		<li>
			<strong>Animal Tales</strong> — Life lessons through enchanting animal
			stories and fables
		</li>
		<li>
			<strong>Classic Tales</strong> — Timeless stories filled with wit, wisdom,
			and humor
		</li>
		<li>
			<strong>Folklore</strong> — Traditional stories from diverse cultural
			heritages around the world
		</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Benefits of Reading Stories</h2>
	<p>
		Reading stories is incredibly beneficial for personal development. It
		sparks imagination and creativity, develops reading habits, and teaches
		valuable life lessons in an engaging way.
	</p>

	<blockquote>
		"Stories are seeds planted in the minds of readers that grow into
		wisdom."
	</blockquote>

